		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The FIRST on those adventure games I wrote included several screens that had water (4 to be exact). I was NOT aware of the fill command, just the line ones. Yes, that's right, I drew the water line by friggen line. It was a truly facepalm worthy moment when I discovered the fill command while working on my second adventure.

		

